303115494.Description: Purposefully-designed storage spaces help you fit and find it all. Get increased loading flexibility with adjustable gallon door bins. 307346119.Title: Maytag 25 cu. ft. Side by Side Refrigerator in Black with Exterior Ice and Water Dispenser
307346119.Description: This side-by-side refrigerator is built tough and easy-to-clean with its fingerprint resistant stainless-steel finish. Built with plenty of storage options, including a specially designed soft freeze bin that puts you in control of the way foods freeze. Put in a pint of ice cream and it's soft enough to scoop. Frozen pizza storage stores two frozen pizza boxes upright and out of the way, so quick meals are an easy grab. The distinct and durable Signature Maytag metal shelf adds a bold look to the inside. With an exterior ice and water dispenser for easy access, plus a 10-year limited parts warranty on the compressor, this side-by-side fridge will keep it all cool for years and years. Color: Black.
